        "name": "GCI < 5% on hemolysis index QoI",
        "description": "Grid Convergence Index (GCI) computed on three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 6.8M, 18.4M cells). GCI on normalized hemolysis index < 5% on the fine-to-medium refinement pair. Achieves Gradation 3."
