      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed per ASME V&V 20. GCI on the primary QoI (normalized hemolysis index NIH) was 3.2% (fine-medium pair), confirming discretization error is well-controlled. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for MRL 2."
