        "name": "Experimental boundary conditions documented and matched",
        "description": "Inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid temperature, and hematocrit documented in FDA GCBP experimental protocol. CFD boundary conditions set to match measured values within ±2% tolerance."
      },
      "rationale": "The FDA GCBP experimental dataset provides fully documented boundary conditions (flow rate 2.5–6 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM, 37°C, Hct 30%). CFD simulations replicate these conditions within measurement uncertainty. Gradation 2 required and achieved."
    },
    {
