      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values at all 5 operating points fall within 18% of experimental means (worst case: 17.8% at 3500 RPM / 2.5 L/min). The ±25% acceptance criterion is met at all points, consistent with published literature scatter for power-law hemolysis models. Gradation 2 achieved."
