      },
      "rationale": "NIH is the FDA-recognized QoI for blood pump hemolysis assessment (FDA Guidance 2021). The relative hemolysis comparison (RH = NIH_device / NIH_predicate) directly supports the regulatory submission decision. QoI relevance is high and well-documented."
