      "rationale": "Numerical solver error (iterative convergence and round-off) is scoped out at MRL 2 for this Class II device. Residuals are monitored and all simulations converged to residuals below 1e-5 for all equations; this level of iterative convergence control is consistent with standard practice and does not require a separate Gradation assessment at MRL 2."
